content.title: RHBA-2025:0305: .NET 9.0 bug fix and enhancement update (Important)
content.description:
.NET Core is a managed-software framework. It implements a subset of the .NET
framework APIs and several new APIs, and it includes a CLR implementation.

Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):

* Update .NET 9.0 to SDK 9.0.102 and Runtime 9.0.1 [rhel-9.5.z] (RHEL-71552)Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):
